author: Lauren Moraski CBS News
title: Caitlyn Jenner's "I Am Cait" gets a season 2
text:
It's official: Caitlyn Jenner will give viewers a chance to see inside her personal life once again.
The reality TV star has signed on for a season 2 of the E! docu-series, "I Am Cait." The first season of the series followed Jenner as she navigated life as a transgender woman -- and the second season will delve even deeper into her transition.
The former Olympian said she is excited to continue the conversation.
I'm looking forward to continuing the conversation. #IAmCait

We are honored Caitlyn has chosen to continue to share her ongoing story with our viewers around the world."
